  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 revision)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This revision elevates the model risk level to 3 following a broader intended use expansion (device now targets paediatric and adult circuits). Ten of thirteen factors are assessed and meet required levels; three factors are carried as not-assessed on the basis that their evaluation is 'beyond the current programme scope', without concrete justification for why the elevated risk level permits deferral.",
