      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must be under documented version control with regression test suite; anomaly tracking must be in place.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 is used under ISO 9001-certified QMS. Version control, regression suite covering 47 benchmark cases, and anomaly tracking via JIRA are all documented. Achieved level exceeds required level for MRL 3."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
