      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy test on canonical internal flow problem must confirm expected convergence rate.",
      "rationale": "Taylor-Couette and lid-driven cavity benchmarks confirm second-order spatial convergence for the pressure-velocity coupling scheme used in the pump model. Required level met."
    },
    {
