      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence to residual < 1e-5 for all equations; mass imbalance < 0.01%.",
      "rationale": "All simulations converged to continuity and momentum residuals below 1e-6. Mass imbalance across the pump domain is 0.003%. Criterion met."
