      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental blood samples must be characterised for donor variability, storage age, and haematocrit; sample-to-sample repeatability must be quantified.",
      "rationale": "Characterisation of test sample variability is deferred as outside the current project scope. Donor variability and storage effects on RBC fragility were not assessed. The team considers this acceptable given the comparative (relative) nature of the acceptance criterion, but no formal evaluation has been documented."
    },
