      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation input parameters (geometry, flow rates, fluid properties) must be demonstrated equivalent to COU conditions through a documented mapping exercise.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency mapping between simulation inputs and the clinical COU envelope has not been completed. The assessment team regards this as a lower-priority activity given the use of the FDA reference geometry, but no documented equivalency analysis exists to support this judgement."
