    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Ten of thirteen credibility factors are assessed and meet or exceed required levels for MRL 3. Three factors (Model inputs, Test samples, Equivalency of input parameters) are carried as not-assessed on the basis that their evaluation falls beyond current programme scope. The team judges the ten assessed factors sufficient to support the Accepted decision, noting that the relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion provides an inherent comparative buffer. No formal risk justification for deferring the three unassessed factors at MRL 3 has been documented.",
